#### This is a README file for SZIP source distribution
#### See rice.h for copyright information


1. To build SZIP Library
========================
              ./configure --prefix=...
              make
              make test
              make install

To build shared and static SZIP Libraries use -s flag with configure.
Default compiler is gcc. Use 

              setenv CC "....." 
              setenv CFLAGS "...."

to set desired compiler and flags. 

2. To run example
==================

First generate generate random image file
 
              burst_szip -msb # 8 1024 16 image.#.in         

where # is the bits_per_pixel value           

Then run example

              example [bits_per_pixel]        

default bits_per_pixel = 8 




 
